We should defs
check it out after

28
00:01:12,823 --> 00:01:13,949
we hit up the
tree house.

29
00:01:14,032 --> 00:01:17,202
Yeah, we gotta get to the bottom
of this hot shower.

30
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:24,334
Hmm.

31
00:01:24,376 --> 00:01:27,212
Does everything seem...
pinker to you?

32
00:01:27,296 --> 00:01:29,506
Home always looks different
after a long trip.

33
00:01:29,590 --> 00:01:32,259
You're seeing it with fresh eyes
and newfound wisdom.

34
00:01:32,342 --> 00:01:34,928
And sometimes there's also a new
strip mall or something.

35
00:01:35,012 --> 00:01:36,555
So everything being pink is
probably not a big deal.

36
00:01:36,597 --> 00:01:38,348
And also, I'm tired.

37
00:01:39,224 --> 00:01:40,684
I like the pink.

38
00:01:40,767 --> 00:01:43,478
Why you worry so much,
worry baby?

39
00:01:43,562 --> 00:01:46,732
Ha, ha, yeah! Why you worry
so much, worry baby?

40
00:01:46,815 --> 00:01:47,941
Don't worry, Finn.

41
00:01:48,025 --> 00:01:51,111
