59
00:02:32,194 --> 00:02:33,445
Fern?!

60
00:02:33,528 --> 00:02:36,365
Who's Fern? I'm Fun the Human.

61
00:02:37,115 --> 00:02:40,077
And I'm Nectr,
the little robot!

62
00:02:40,535 --> 00:02:43,830
I'm Shelby the Worm...
the gummy worm!

63
00:02:44,164 --> 00:02:45,874
Welcome, strangers.

64
00:02:45,957 --> 00:02:48,210
It's so cool that you're
inside our house.

65
00:02:48,293 --> 00:02:50,629
Dude, when did you guys
turn into candy?

66
00:02:50,671 --> 00:02:55,175
We've always been candy,
you silly billy bean!

67
00:02:55,425 --> 00:02:57,511
Ohh, okay. I get it.

68
00:02:57,594 --> 00:02:59,846
