as an equal.

76
00:03:13,944 --> 00:03:16,613
You were supposed to take care
of Ooo while I was gone.

77
00:03:16,697 --> 00:03:18,156
What happened with that?

78
00:03:18,323 --> 00:03:19,449
What?

79
00:03:19,533 --> 00:03:21,743
You used to be this volatile
plant boy. Remember?

80
00:03:21,993 --> 00:03:24,746
Really? Well, I'm candy now.

81
00:03:24,830 --> 00:03:27,165
And I'm in control
of my emotions.

82
00:03:27,416 --> 00:03:28,750
I'm in control, too...

83
00:03:28,834 --> 00:03:30,293
of my body!

84
00:03:30,377 --> 00:03:31,670
[ Laughs ]

85
00:03:31,753 --> 00:03:33,630
Wow, gummy Shelby's
a lot of fun.

86
00:03:33,714 --> 00:03:36,049
I think I'm okay with
Candyworld.

87
00:03:36,133 --> 00:03:38,593
No way. Let's talk to PB.

88
00:03:38,677 --> 00:03:41,221
I'm sure this is all one of her
experiments gone wrong.

89
00:03:41,263 --> 00:03:43,181
You seem upset, friend.

90
00:03:43,265 --> 00:03:45,517
The tower will fix you right up.

91
00:03:46,309 --> 00:03:47,644
