Oh, boy!

94
00:03:51,148 --> 00:03:53,400
Let's run outside!

95
00:03:53,483 --> 00:03:56,403
[ Bell dinging continues ]
[ Nectr whirring ]

96
00:03:56,903 --> 00:04:00,323
[ Wheels squeaking ]

97
00:04:04,035 --> 00:04:06,329
Hello! It's me!

98
00:04:06,413 --> 00:04:07,831
Lemonpink!

99
00:04:07,914 --> 00:04:09,624
He was inside the lemon.

100
00:04:09,708 --> 00:04:11,710
Mm! Drink up, babies!

101
00:04:11,752 --> 00:04:13,670
