Squeeze!

102
00:04:13,754 --> 00:04:15,505
[ Laughing ]

103
00:04:15,589 --> 00:04:18,133
I used to have a lot of fear
and sadness,

104
00:04:18,216 --> 00:04:21,386
but now I'm fine!

105
00:04:21,470 --> 00:04:22,804
Hey, I want some of that.

106
00:04:22,888 --> 00:04:25,140
No. That is body juice.

107
00:04:25,223 --> 00:04:28,059
Hmm? What's that?

108
00:04:28,143 --> 00:04:31,021
Do you spurn my fluids?

109
00:04:31,062 --> 00:04:32,147
(\\[oR

110
00:04:32,230 --> 00:04:35,734
Maybe someone's feeling
a little sour!

111
00:04:35,817 --> 00:04:37,152
Wuh-whoa!

112
00:04:37,235 --> 00:04:39,321
You know what sours get.

113
00:04:39,488 --> 00:04:41,281
Sours get the tower!

114
00:04:41,323 --> 00:04:44,576
Candies: Sours get the tower!
Sours get the tower!

115
00:04:44,659 --> 00:04:48,371
[ Splat ]
Sours get the tower!
Sours get the tower!

116
00:04:48,455 --> 00:04:50,749
Come on, Jake.
Let's go see Bubblegum.

117
00:04:50,957 --> 00:04:53,585
