And Fern is, like,
laughing and joking around.

127
00:05:18,819 --> 00:05:20,695
Maybe they don't need you
to fix them.

128
00:05:21,738 --> 00:05:22,697
Hmm.

129
00:05:23,323 --> 00:05:25,575
