134
00:05:36,586 --> 00:05:39,589
Hey, buddy, what are you
doing out... uh...

135
00:05:39,965 --> 00:05:42,592
Hey! You're meat!

136
00:05:42,717 --> 00:05:44,970
Yes, I'm meat. [ Sniffles ]

137
00:05:45,053 --> 00:05:47,472
