about all this.

153
00:06:26,011 --> 00:06:28,346
She's not in the Candy Kingdom.

154
00:06:28,430 --> 00:06:31,057
She's in the Terrible Tower.

155
00:06:31,808 --> 00:06:32,976
Look!

156
00:06:36,730 --> 00:06:39,149
Come on, Jake.
That's kind of weird, right?

157
00:06:39,316 --> 00:06:41,318
I think it's magnificent!

158
00:06:41,401 --> 00:06:44,738
Sweet P! Yoo-hoo!

159
00:06:44,821 --> 00:06:46,990
We brought some rollers

160
00:06:47,073 --> 00:06:50,410
and a bucket
of sweet juicy caramel.

161
00:06:50,660 --> 00:06:53,788
Let's get you back to normal.

162
00:06:53,872 --> 00:06:57,375
But, Mama, I am normal!

163
00:06:57,459 --> 00:07:01,379
Just sit tight there
like a windowpane,

164
00:07:01,588 --> 00:07:05,592
and you'll be back to normal
like a windowpane.

165
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:08,386
