166
00:07:08,470 --> 00:07:11,806
Hmm. Okay, you're right.
This is pretty freaky-deaky.

167
00:07:12,182 --> 00:07:15,226
I'm gonna go now. [ Crying ]

168
00:07:15,518 --> 00:07:17,312
