at Lady's.

178
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:39,834
[ Sniffs ]

179
00:07:39,918 --> 00:07:41,878
Ooh. Somethin' smells nice.

180
00:07:41,962 --> 00:07:43,797
Nice and toasty.

181
00:07:44,923 --> 00:07:46,341
[ Roars ]

182
00:07:46,424 --> 00:07:47,676
All: S'more!

183
00:07:47,759 --> 00:07:49,010
Stay back, S'more!

184
00:07:49,219 --> 00:07:51,012
Jake: Get it! Get it!
Get it! Get it!

185
00:07:51,096 --> 00:07:54,224
[ Growls ]
[ Laughs ] Whoa, dudes.

186
00:07:55,558 --> 00:07:57,143
I was just playin'.

187
00:07:57,227 --> 00:07:59,771
All: What?! Marceline!

188
00:07:59,854 --> 00:08:03,108
[ Giggles ]
No, it's Marshmaline...

189
00:08:03,191 --> 00:08:04,943
the Campfire Queen.

190
00:08:05,026 --> 00:08:06,236
Mar--
Marsha--

191
00:08:06,319 --> 00:08:07,529
Marsha-- Mars--
Marsha --

192
00:08:07,612 --> 00:08:08,822
Marcine.
Mar-- Mar--

193
00:08:08,905 --> 00:08:10,865
Marsh-- Marshmi--
Marshman-- My--

194
00:08:10,949 --> 00:08:11,992
Would you like to hear a song?

195
00:08:12,075 --> 00:08:14,786
I've written just the ditty
that'll cheer up anyone

196
00:08:14,869 --> 00:08:17,247
