or responsibility.

197
00:08:17,372 --> 00:08:20,500
Yay! I love Marshmaline songs!

198
00:08:20,542 --> 00:08:23,128
No time for tunes.
Do you know where Bonnie is?

199
00:08:23,211 --> 00:08:25,463
Of course! Follow me.

200
00:08:26,339 --> 00:08:30,719
[ Humming "Greensleeves" ]

201
00:08:30,927 --> 00:08:35,348
[ Humming continues ]

202
00:08:37,851 --> 00:08:40,937
[ Humming ends ]

203
00:08:41,312 --> 00:08:43,857
