204
00:08:43,940 --> 00:08:45,817
She's everywhere.

205
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:49,529
[ Rumbling ]

206
00:08:49,612 --> 00:08:52,490
Good tidings to you,
my friends.

207
00:08:52,574 --> 00:08:53,658
[ Gasps |
[ Gasps |

208
00:08:53,742 --> 00:08:55,201
Yahoo!

209
00:08:55,285 --> 00:08:57,120
