210
00:08:57,412 --> 00:08:59,205
Oh, this? [ Giggles ]

211
00:08:59,372 --> 00:09:02,083
I've become what I was always
meant to become --

212
00:09:02,167 --> 00:09:05,128
a pure candy elemental.

213
00:09:05,253 --> 00:09:07,172
[ Vomits ]

214
00:09:07,255 --> 00:09:11,259
[ Laughs, cheering ]

215
00:09:11,301 --> 00:09:13,636
[ Belches ] 'Scuse me.

216
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:15,472
What about Tree Trunks
and Lemongrab

217
00:09:15,555 --> 00:09:17,432
and Marceline
and everyone else?

218
00:09:17,515 --> 00:09:19,601
I fixed 'em, obviously.

219
00:09:19,684 --> 00:09:22,020
Fixed 'em?
But they're your friends!

220
00:09:22,062 --> 00:09:24,647
Those aren't
mutually exclusive concepts.

221
00:09:24,731 --> 00:09:26,357
That means it's fine.

222
00:09:26,441 --> 00:09:28,443
No, it's not fine.

223
00:09:28,526 --> 00:09:29,986
Don't fret.

224
00:09:30,070 --> 00:09:32,072
I can fix you, too.

225
00:09:32,113 --> 00:09:35,075
[ Squishing ]

226
00:09:35,158 --> 00:09:36,785
Aah! Aah! Aah!

227
00:09:36,868 --> 00:09:38,536
I can feel my bones
turning gummy!

228
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:39,788
Me, too!

229
00:09:39,871 --> 00:09:41,039
We gotta get out of here
before --

230
00:09:41,081 --> 00:09:41,706
Oof!
Hugs!

231
00:09:41,790 --> 00:09:44,167
I'm connected to all candy

232
00:09:44,250 --> 00:09:46,377
