233
00:09:46,461 --> 00:09:50,965
Once you're candy,
you'll be part of me, too!

234
00:09:51,049 --> 00:09:53,510
No! That plan sucks!

235
00:09:53,593 --> 00:09:55,095
[ Speaking indistinctly ]
Oh, my gosh!

236
00:09:55,178 --> 00:09:57,305
Aah! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
I'm sorry!

237
00:09:57,388 --> 00:09:58,890
I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
I'm sorry!
Oow!

238
00:09:58,973 --> 00:10:00,141
Skyhooks!

239
00:10:00,892 --> 00:10:02,185
