240
00:10:03,311 --> 00:10:04,938
Hold on to me, bro!

241
00:10:05,605 --> 00:10:07,148
No!

242
00:10:07,232 --> 00:10:09,984
Wait, we forgot... BMO!

243
00:10:10,068 --> 00:10:12,904
Goodbye, boys!
It's better this way!

244
00:10:13,154 --> 00:10:14,948
[ Beeping ]

245
00:10:15,031 --> 00:10:18,076
