253
00:10:34,467 --> 00:10:35,927
Looks like we got away

254
00:10:36,010 --> 00:10:37,720
before the candy curse
became permanent.

255
00:10:38,221 --> 00:10:41,474
That's right.
My skyhooks saved the day.

256
00:10:41,558 --> 00:10:43,476
Thanks for getting us out
of there, Simon.

257
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:47,689
Aw, I can't take all the credit.
It's all thanks to my skyhooks.

258
00:10:47,772 --> 00:10:50,275
Hey, why are you even up here?

259
00:10:50,358 --> 00:10:53,945
We live here now,
me and the skyhooks.

260
00:10:54,028 --> 00:10:57,198
Finn, you gotta see this.

261
00:10:59,659 --> 00:11:00,618
[ Gasps |

262
00:11:00,702 --> 00:11:02,370
Oh...

my...

263
00:11:02,787 --> 00:11:05,206
but...

